"ID":"20240513171439-pwdo0fj","Type":"NodeSuperBlock","Properties":{"id":"20240513171439-pwdo0fj","updated":"20240513171946"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeSuperBlockOpenMarker"},{"Type":"NodeSuperBlockLayoutMarker","Data":"col"},{"ID":"20240513171437-mme3d99","Type":"NodeSuperBlock","Properties":{"id":"20240513171437-mme3d99","updated":"20240513171946"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeSuperBlockOpenMarker"},{"Type":"NodeSuperBlockLayoutMarker","Data":"row"},{"ID":"20240513171231-cfqr01x","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240513171231-cfqr01x","updated":"20240513171438"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"后来出现了多重采样抗锯齿 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-memo","TextMarkInlineMemoContent":"Multisample Anti-aliasing","TextMarkTextContent":"MSAA"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，借鉴了 SSAA 背后的理念，但却以更加高效的方式实现了抗锯齿。"}]},{"ID":"20240513171241-82jmv1n","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240513171241-82jmv1n","style":"color: var(--b3-card-info-color);background-color: var(--b3-card-info-background);","updated":"20240513171438"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"多重采样：将单一的采样点变为多个采样点。以特定图案排列的几个"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"parent-style":"color: var(--b3-card-info-color);background-color: var(--b3-card-info-background);"},"TextMarkType":"inline-memo","TextMarkInlineMemoContent":"Subsample","TextMarkTextContent":"子采样点"},{"Type":"NodeKramdownSpanIAL","Data":"{: parent-style=\"color: var(--b3-card-info-color);background-color: var(--b3-card-info-background);\"}"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（默认 4 个）决定像素的遮盖度。"}]},{"ID":"20240513171400-sthlef3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240513171400-sthlef3","style":"color: var(--b3-card-warning-color);background-color: var(--b3-card-warning-background);","updated":"20240513171438"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"颜色缓冲的大小会随着子采样点的增加而增加。"}]},{"Type":"NodeSuperBlockCloseMarker"}]},{"ID":"20240513171432-65g3bt8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240513171432-65g3bt8","updated":"20240513171744"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"Pasted image 20230913155504"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/Pasted image 20230913155504-20240513171432-h77zy5p.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"}]},{"Type":"NodeSuperBlockCloseMarker"}]},{"ID":"20240513171938-5nyn3uj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240513171938-5nyn3uj","updated":"20240513171946"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"上图中4个采样点中只有2个被遮盖住了，这个像素的颜色将会是三角形颜色与其他两个采样点的颜色（在这里是无色）的平均值，最终形成一种淡蓝色。"}]},{"ID":"20240513172144-pppovh9","Type":"NodeSuperBlock","Properties":{"id":"20240513172144-pppovh9","updated":"20240513172301"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeSuperBlockOpenMarker"},{"Type":"NodeSuperBlockLayoutMarker","Data":"col"},{"ID":"20240513171632-qpaeusl","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20240513171632-qpaeusl","updated":"20240513172301"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20240513172114-dhjje0c","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240513172114-dhjje0c","updated":"20240513172114"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"MSAA真正的工作方式是，无论三角形遮盖了多少个子采样点，每个图元中每个像素只运行"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"一次"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"片段着色器。"}]},{"ID":"20240513172114-q6fg4mm","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240513172114-q6fg4mm","updated":"20240513172114"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"片段着色器所使用的顶点数据会插值到每个像素的"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"中心"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，所得到的结果颜色会被储存在每个被遮盖住的子采样点中。"}]},{"ID":"20240513172114-q9mj5ci","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240513172114-q9mj5ci","updated":"20240513172114"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"当颜色缓冲的子样本被图元的所有颜色填满时，所有的这些颜色将会在每个像素内部平均化。"}]},{"ID":"20240513172301-6qa9mm6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240513172301-6qa9mm6","updated":"20240513172301"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"对于每个像素来说，越少的子采样点被三角形所覆盖，那么它受到三角形的影响就越小。三角形的不平滑边缘被稍浅的颜色所包围后，从远处观察时就会显得更加平滑了。"}]}]},{"ID":"20240513172137-khekmlb","Type":"NodeSuperBlock","Properties":{"id":"20240513172137-khekmlb","style":"width: 25%; flex: 0 0 auto;"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeSuperBlockOpenMarker"},{"Type":"NodeSuperBlockLayoutMarker","Data":"col"},{"ID":"20240513172118-pb97dyh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240513172118-pb97dyh","updated":"20240513172118"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"Pasted image 20230913155714"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/Pasted image 20230913155714-20240513172118-hjy9muh.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"}]},{"ID":"20240513172131-rznxkgf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240513172131-rznxkgf","updated":"20240513172223"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"Pasted image 20230913155728"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/Pasted image 20230913155728-20240513172131-fy9u82a.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"}]},{"Type":"NodeSuperBlockCloseMarker"}]},{"Type":"NodeSuperBlockCloseMarker"}]},{"ID":"20240513172236-1itqj9q","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240513172236-1itqj9q","style":"color: var(--b3-card-info-color);background-color: var(--b3-card-info-background);","updated":"20240513172413"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"深度和模板测试也能够使用多个采样点，相应的深度和模板缓冲的大小会乘子采样点的个数。\n  对深度测试来说，每个顶点的深度值会在运行深度测试之前被插值到各个子样本中。\n  对模板测试来说，我们对每个子样本，而不是每个像素，存储一个模板值。"}]},{"ID":"20240513172434-shhqdu7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240513172434-shhqdu7","updated":"20240513172449"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"在 OpenGL 中使用多重采样，要求每个像素中存储大于 1 个颜色的颜色缓冲，为一个窗口绑定一个包含 N 个样本的多重采样缓冲可通过 GLFW 完成。"}]},{"ID":"20240513172450-o3auhno","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240513172450-o3auhno","updated":"20240513172450"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"在窗口创建之前设置："}]},{"ID":"20240513172429-hvmb33e","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20240513172429-hvmb33e","updated":"20240513172429"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"Yysr"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"// 包含 4 个样本的颜色缓冲\nglfwWindowHint(GLFW_SAMPLES, 4);\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20240513172429-qr97h17","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240513172429-qr97h17","updated":"20240513172429"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"之后，在 OpenGL 中启用多重采样即可，具体细节在 OpenGL 光栅器中已经实现，无需过多关心"}]},{"ID":"20240513172429-hyiv3we","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20240513172429-hyiv3we","updated":"20240513172429"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"Yysr"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"glEnable(GL_MULTISAMPLE);\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]}]}